Example workspace (no auth)

This file shows example layouts produced by the CLI when authentication is disabled (no auth). It includes both microservice (Docker / PM2) and monolith outputs so you can compare.

Microservice (no auth)

my-workspace/
  services/
    gateway/
    health-service/
  shared/
    config/
    utils/
  package.json
  README.md
  .env.example

Notes:
- For Docker mode the workspace includes `docker-compose.yml` at the repository root.
- For PM2 (nodocker) mode the workspace includes `pm2.config.js` at the repository root.
- If auth is enabled during generation, an additional `auth-service/` will appear under `services/`.

